### Architecture Summary

```
Frontend (Next.js) ──▶ Backend (FastAPI) ──▶ Dapr Sidecar ──▶ Kafka
                                                    │
                            ┌───────────────────────┴───────────────────────┐
                            ▼                                               ▼
                    Recurring Service                               Notification Service
                    (task.completed → create next)                  (reminders → log)
```

### Components

| Component | Port | Dapr App ID | Language |
|-----------|------|-------------|----------|
| Backend | 8000 | todo-backend | Python 3.11 |
| Frontend | 3000 | todo-frontend | TypeScript |
| Notification | 8001 | notification-service | Python 3.11 |
| Recurring | 8002 | recurring-service | Python 3.11 |

### Kafka Topics

| Topic | Producers | Consumers |
|-------|-----------|-----------|
